Sentencas: Highly electrochemical performance and CO2 durability are two main aims for exploring novel cathodes in solid oxide fuel cells operated at intermediate temperatures.
Titulo: High-Performance and CO2-Durable Composite Cathodes toward Electrocatalytic Oxygen Reduction: Ce0.8Sm0.2O1.9 Nanoparticle-Decorated Double Perovskite EuBa0.5Sr0.5Co2O5+δ

Sentencas: With respect to these issues, herein, Ce0.8Sm0.2O1.9 nanoparticles (SDC-n) (mean particle size of similar to 100 nm) are incorporated into a double perovskite EuBa0.5Sr0.5Co2O5+delta (EBSC) cathode by the mechanical mixing method.
Titulo: High-Performance and CO2-Durable Composite Cathodes toward Electrocatalytic Oxygen Reduction: Ce0.8Sm0.2O1.9 Nanoparticle-Decorated Double Perovskite EuBa0.5Sr0.5Co2O5+δ

Sentencas: We systematically evaluate the positive effects of SDC-n on electrode characteristics, electrochemical performance, and long-term durability of EuBa0.5Sr0.5Co2O5+delta-xCe(0.8)Sm(0.2)O(1.9)
Titulo: High-Performance and CO2-Durable Composite Cathodes toward Electrocatalytic Oxygen Reduction: Ce0.8Sm0.2O1.9 Nanoparticle-Decorated Double Perovskite EuBa0.5Sr0.5Co2O5+δ

Sentencas: (EBSC-xSDC-n, x = 0-40 wt %) composite materials, via complementary phase and structure analyses, dilatometric and electrical conductivity measurements, electrochemical impedance spectroscopy (EIS), and fuel cell tests.
Titulo: High-Performance and CO2-Durable Composite Cathodes toward Electrocatalytic Oxygen Reduction: Ce0.8Sm0.2O1.9 Nanoparticle-Decorated Double Perovskite EuBa0.5Sr0.5Co2O5+δ

Sentencas: Among all composite cathodes, EBSC-30SDC-n has the lowest polarization resistance (0.061 Omega cm(2), 700 degrees C) and a significantly better CO2 tolerance than the pristine EBSC cathode, as confirmed by EIS results obtained in a gas mixture of CO2 and air (involving 1, 5, or 10% CO2).
Titulo: High-Performance and CO2-Durable Composite Cathodes toward Electrocatalytic Oxygen Reduction: Ce0.8Sm0.2O1.9 Nanoparticle-Decorated Double Perovskite EuBa0.5Sr0.5Co2O5+δ

Sentencas: The peak power density of 1185 mW cm(-2) is achieved in a complete single cell employing the EBSC-30SDC-n cathode at 700 degrees C.
Titulo: High-Performance and CO2-Durable Composite Cathodes toward Electrocatalytic Oxygen Reduction: Ce0.8Sm0.2O1.9 Nanoparticle-Decorated Double Perovskite EuBa0.5Sr0.5Co2O5+δ

Sentencas: The results promise their potential application for high-performance cathodes.
